Invocation Name: multiplication tables
des:
Easy and effective learning method to get children to learn and study multiplication tables.

Children can learn by listening and seeing and can also answer the multiplication tables at the moment the child decides to be evaluated.

It is wonderful and children will enjoy it!

Multiplication tables is compatible with Echo and Echo Show
